item.dc:creator: @Kidpaparoach Kidpaparoach
item.description:
@Kidpaparoach wrote:

[quote=“LilXCj, post:32, topic:438259”][quote author=Kidpaparoach link=topic=540977.msg3967448#msg3967448 date=1333848734]

$7k for a 99, $7k could buy them better things than rs. They’d prob buy an account and gold… not this. I estimate no more than 5 people will actually but it to get a 99 from a lowish level and they will be the types of people that take the money of there parents for it.
Complete stupidity unless you have 100m+ irl cash then its not so bad, why waste time on things you don’t wanna do when you can buy it.
[/quote]about 85% of the high level accounts that are bought are recovered. Because:

  1. they were recovered/hacked accounts in the first place
  2. People are selfish pigs

even if these rich kids spent 7k$ on it to get the skills through sof then it would be the smarter/legit way

More than 85%:P, I personally have never heard of an account being sold and not recovered from someone I know. Most likely 2 me thinks:P

I heard that 43% of statistics are made up.[/quote]
I heard it was a different % lololol, is your statistic made up?
